NAME
    MooX::Types::MooseLike::Numeric - Moo types for numbers

SYNOPSIS
        package MyPackage;
        use Moo;
        use MooX::Types::MooseLike::Numeric qw(PositiveInt);

        has "daily_breathes" => (
            isa => PositiveInt
        );

DESCRIPTION
    adapted from MooseX::Types::Common::Numeric

TYPES (subroutines)
    Available types are listed below.

    PositiveNum
    PositiveOrZeroNum
    PositiveInt
    PositiveOrZeroInt
    NegativeNum
    NegativeOrZeroNum
    NegativeInt
    NegativeOrZeroInt
    SingleDigit

